[Stop/Restart Timer (L3=Stop Timer, R3=Restart Timer)]
author=HackFreak
description=Note: It will allow you to stop the timer and restart it. A weird side effect of this code though is that it disables the cpu racers AI. When activating the code in drag races,press L3 and wait for the cpu racers cars to stop moving. After they have stopped moving,press R3. You can then continue the race without worrying about them. When using it in circuit and quick races,just press L3 and continue on with the race. Then when you reach the finish line,press R3. Do not use this code in sprint races. You and the cpu racers cars will just slow down and stop. Should also work on the PAL version.
patch=1,EE,D02F8350,extended,58B0D56B
patch=1,EE,EE19A44E,extended,50B5D466
patch=1,EE,D02F8350,extended,58B0D569
patch=1,EE,EE19A44E,extended,E12ADF96

